########################################
# Iridium 9603N Solar Beacon Prototype #
########################################

A breadboard prototype for a Solar Powered Iridium 9603N Beacon.

Power for the beacon is provided by a PowerFilm MPT3.6-150 solar panel.

Power for the Iridium 9603N is provided by a Linear Technology LTC3225EDDB supercapacitor charger.

See Iridium_9603N_Solar_Beacon_Prototype.pdf for a full description of the project:
https://github.com/PaulZC/Iridium_9603N_Solar_Beacon/blob/master/Iridium_9603N_Solar_Beacon_Prototype.pdf

The Arduino code can be found in Iridium9603NSolarBeaconPrototype
https://github.com/PaulZC/Iridium_9603N_Solar_Beacon/tree/master/Iridium9603NSolarBeaconPrototype

A Fritzing hook-up diagram can be found in Iridium_9603N_Solar_Beacon_Prototype_Fritzing.png
https://github.com/PaulZC/Iridium_9603N_Solar_Beacon/blob/master/Iridium_9603N_Solar_Beacon_Prototype_Fritzing.png

This project is distributed under a Creative Commons Attribution + Share-alike (BY-SA) licence.

Enjoy!

Paul
